                     <interp inst="t17820703-8-verdict42" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder5s"></interp>
               GUILTY of stealing to the value of 3 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice BULLER.</p>
